\c 9
\s Kubwinya kwaJesu pagomo
\p
\v 1 Zvino wakati kwavari: Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: Vamwe varipo kunavamire pano, vasingazoraviri rufu, vasati vavona vushe bwaMwari bwuchivuya nesimba.
\v 2 Mushure mazuva matanhatu, Jesu akatora Petro, naJokobho, naJohwani, akavatungamirira mugomo refu, vari voga; akashandurwa pamberi pavo.
\v 3 Nguvo dzake dzikapenya, dzikachenesesa zvikuru semagada echando; zvokuti hakunomusuki pano panyika, ungagona kudzichenesa \add dzikadaro\add*.
\v 4 Zvino kwakavonekwa kwavari Eria naMozisi, vachitaurirana naJesu.
\v 5 Petro akapindura akati kunaJesu: Rabhi, zvakanaka kuti tive pano; ngativake matumba matatu, rimwe renyu, rimwe raMozisi, rimwe raEria.
\v 6 Nokuti wakanga asingazivi chokutaura, nokuti vakatya zvikuru.
\v 7 Zvino gore rikavuya rikavafukidza, inzwi rikabuda mugore, richiti: Uyu Mwanakomana wangu unodikanwa, mumunzwei!
\v 8 Kamwe-kamwe, vakati varinga-ringa, havana kuzovona munhu, asi Jesu bedzi anavo.
\v 9 Zvino vakati vachiburuka mugomo, akavaraira kuti varege kuvudza munhu zvavakanga vavona kusvikira Mwanakomana womunhu amuka kuvakafa.
\v 10 Vakarichengeta shoko iro, vachiita nyaya pakati pavo, kuti kumuka kwavakafa chinyiko?
\v 11 Vakamubvunza, vachiti: Vanyori vanotaurireiko vachiti, Eria unofanira kutanga kuvuya?
\v 12 Akapindura akati kwavari: Eria uchatanga kuvuya hake, avandudze zvinhu zvose, asi kwakagonyorwa seiko zvoMwanakomana womunhu, kuti uchatambudzika zvikuru nokuzvidzwa?
\v 13 Asi ndinoti kwamuri, Eria wakatosvika, vakamuitira zvose pavakanga vachida napo, sezvazvakanyorwa pamusoro pake.
\s Jesu unoporesa mukomana unezvipusha
\p
\v 14 Vakati vasvika kuvadzidzi, vakavona vanhu gurumwandira guru, vakavakomba, navanyori vachipikisana navo.
\v 15 Pakarepo vazhinji vose vakati vachimuvona vakashamiswa kwazvo, vakamhanyira kwaari, vakamukwazisa.
\v 16 Akabvunza vanyori akati: Munopikisaneiko navo?
\v 17 Mumwe wavazhinji akamupindura, akati: Mudzidzisi, ndavuya kwamuri nomwanakomana wangu, unomweya wembeveve;
\v 18 pose paanomubata, unomubvambura, achipupuma furo, achigeda-geda meno, vuye unowonda kwazvo; ndakataura navadzidzi venyu kuti vaubudise, vakasagona.
\v 19 Akavapindura, akati: Haiwa, rudzi rusingatendi, ndichagara nemi kusvikira riniko? Ndichakuitirai moyo murefu kusvikira riniko Vuyai naye kwandiri.
\v 20 Vakavuya naye kwaari; wakati achimuvona, pakarepo mweya ukamubvundisa; akawira pasi, akakunguruka, achipupuma furo.
\v 21 Zvino akabvunza baba vake \add akati\add*: Yava nguva yakadiniko kubvira izvozvi zvichimuwira? Akati: Kubva pavuduku bwake.
\v 22 Kazhinji wakamuwisira mumoto nomumvura, kuti umuparadze; asi kana muchigona kuita chinhu, mutinzwire tsitsi, mutibatsire.
\v 23 Jesu akati kwaari: Kana iwe uchigona kutenda, zvinhu zvose zvingaitika kunounotenda.
\v 24 Zvino pakarepo baba vomwana vakadanidzira nemisodzi, vachiti: Ndinotenda Ishe, ndibatsirei pakusatenda kwangu.
\v 25 Zvino Jesu wakati achivona vanhu vazhinji vachimhanyirana pamwe chete, akadzivisa mweya wetsina, akati kwauri: \add Iwe\add*, mweya wembeveve namatsi, ndinokuraira kuti ubve maari, urege kupindazve maari!
\v 26 Ukadanidzira, ukamubvundisa zvikuru ukabuda maari; akaita somunhu wakafa, nokudaro vazhinji vakati: Wafa.
\v 27 Asi Jesu wakabata ruvoko rwake, akamusimudza, iye akasimuka.
\v 28 Zvino wakati apinda mumba, vadzidzi vake vakamubvunza pachivande vachiti: Isu takanga tisingagoni neiko kuubudisa?
\v 29 Akati kwavari: Rudzi urwu harungatongobudi nechinhu, asi nokunyengetera nekutsanya.
\s Jesu unotaura zvorufu rwake nokumuka kwake.
\p
\v 30 Vakabva ipapo, vakagura neGariri, akaramba kuti zvizikamwe nomunhu.
\v 31 Nokuti wakadzidzisa vadzidzi vake, akati kwavari: Mwanakomana womunhu uchaiswa mumavoko avanhu, vachamuvuraya; kana avurawa, uchamukazve mazuva matatu apfuvura.
\v 32 Asi havana kunzwisisa shoko iro, vakatya kumubvunza.
\s Mukuru pavushe bwokudenga, nezvigumbuso.
\p
\v 33 Zvino wakasvika Kapenaume; akati ava mumba, akavabvunza, \add achiti\add*: Makanga muchiita nyaya yeiko munzira?
\v 34 Vakaramba vanyerere, nokuti vakanga vaita nharo pakati pavo munzira, kuti mukuru ndiani.
\v 35 Ipapo akagara pasi, akadana vanegumi navaviri, akati kwavari: Kana munhu achida kuva wokutanga, uchazova weshure kunavose nomuranda wavose.
\v 36 Akatora mwana muduku, akamuisa pakati pavo; akati amufungatira mumavoko, akati kwavari:
\v 37 Aninani unogamuchira mumwe wavaduku vakadai nezita rangu, unondigamuchireni; aninani unondigamuchira ini, haandigamuchiri ini, asi uyo wakandituma.
\v 38 Zvino Johwani akamupindura achiti: Mudzidzisi, tavona munhu achibudisa mweya yakaipa muzita renyu, asingatiteveri tikamudzivisa, nokuti haana kutitevera.
\v 39 Asi Jesu akati: Musamudzivisa, nokuti hakunomunhu ungaita basa resimba nezita rangu, ungakurumidza kutaura zvakaipa pamusoro pangu.
\v 40 Nokuti usingapesani nesu, unesu.
\v 41 Nokuti aninani unokunwisai mukombe wemvura muzita rangu, nemhaka yokuti muri vaKristu, zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri, haana kurashikirwa nomubairo wake.
\v 42 Aninani unogumbusa mumwe wavaduku ava vanotenda kwandiri, zvirinani kwaari kuti guyo guru risungirirwe pamutsipa wake, akandirwe mugungwa.
\v 43 Kana ruvoko rwako ruchikugumbusa, urugure; zvirinani kwauri kuti upinde muvupenyu uri chirema, pakuenda mugehena, mumoto usingadzimwi, unamavoko maviri.
\v 44 Apo pasingafi honye yavo, napasingadzimwi moto.
\v 45 Kana rutsoko rwako ruchikugumbusa, urugure; zvirinani kwauri kuti upinde muvupenyu uchikamhina, pakukandirwa mugehena, unetsoka mbiri.
\v 46 Apo pasingafi honye yavo, napasingadzimwi moto.
\v 47 Zvino kana ziso rako richikugumbusa, uridzure; zvirinani kwauri kuti upinde muvushe bwaMwari uneziso rimwe, pakukandirwa mugehena remoto, unameso maviri.
\v 48 Apo pasingafi honye yavo, napasingadzimwi moto.
\v 49 Nokuti mumwe nomumwe ucharungwa nomoto nechibayiro chimwe nechimwe chicharungwa nemunyu.
\v 50 Munyu wakanaka; asi kana munyu usichavavi, mungaurunga neiko? Ivai nomunyu mukati menyu muve norugare pakati penyu.
